Package org.hibernate.search.mapper.pojo.extractor.builtin

Class BuiltinContainerExtractors

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.search.mapper.pojo.extractor.builtin.BuiltinContainerExtractors
  • public class BuiltinContainerExtractors
extends Object
